item.title: CVE-2023-35055|2023-10-11T17:00:06.915Z -- yifan -- yf325
item.description: A buffer overflow vulnerability exists in the httpd next_page functionality of Yifan YF325 v1.0_20221108. A specially crafted network request can lead to command execution. An attacker can send a network request to trigger this vulnerability.This buffer overflow is in the next_page parameter in the gozila_cgi function.
